          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-copy-2-1678455224138-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>koftas</strong> to one side of a baking tray (use <strong>baking paper</strong> to avoid mess!)</p><p>Add the <strong>onion wedges </strong>to the other side and drizzle with a little <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 15 min or until the koftas are cooked through (no pink meat!) and the onion is slightly charred – these are your <strong>spiced koftas</strong> and <strong>roasted onion</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
