      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>natural yoghurt </strong>and <strong>harissa paste </strong>(can’t handle the heat? Go easy!) to a small bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Stir once or twice to swirl the harissa through the yoghurt<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>harissa-marbled yoghurt</strong></p>",
