      "instruction": "<p>Once the koftas are almost done, add your <strong>tortillas</strong> to a baking tray</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 2-3 min or until they're warmed through (alternatively, add them to a plate and pop in the microwave for 20 secs on high!)</p>",
